{"arkId":"cl020022189","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl020022189","modified ":"2025-08-19","title":"Le D\u00e9part du Tr\u00e9port","titleComplement":null,"denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Le D\u00e9part du Tr\u00e9port"}],"displayDateCreated":"vers 1846","currentLocation":"R\u00e9serve des grands albums \/ Album Pingret Edouard \/ Folio 3 \/ rapport\u00e9 au recto","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1846,"endYear":"","text":null,"type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"PINGRET Edouard Henri Th\u00e9ophile","attributionLevel":"attribution actuelle","linkType":"original","dates":[{"date":"1788","place":"","type":"date 1"},{"date":"1875","place":"","type":"date 2"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q274426"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 6952, Recto","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"Inv. fran\u00e7ais, t. XIII 1344","type":"Num\u00e9ros de catalogues"},{"value":"vol.21, p.320","type":"R\u00e9f\u00e9rence de l\u0027inventaire manuscrit"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Arts graphiques","printsDrawingsEntity":"Cabinet des dessins","printsDrawingsCollection":"Fonds des dessins et miniatures","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Description de l\u0027album :Album factice de 109 folii num\u00e9rot\u00e9s de 1 \u00e0 111 (RF 6952 \u00e0 RF 7108, le RF 7052 d\u00e9tach\u00e9) sur lesquels sont coll\u00e9s des dessins originaux, des lithographies, cartes et extraits de journaux relatifs au voyage de Louis-Philippe au ch\u00e2teau de Windsor en 1844. Un manuscrit de 117 feuillets num\u00e9rot\u00e9s l\u0027accompagne. L\u0027album est pr\u00e9paratoire au recueil de lithographies : \u0027Voyage de S.M. Louis-Philippe 1er, roi des Fran\u00e7ais au ch\u00e2teau de Windsor\u0027, publi\u00e9 \u00e0 Paris par Pingret et \u00e0 Londres par Ackermann, le 31 janvier 1846. Il connu un succ\u00e8s identique au recueil de Skelton \u0027Le Ch\u00e2teau d\u0027Eu illustr\u00e9, depuis son origine en 912 jusqu\u0027au voyage de sa majest\u00e9 Victoria, [...] , Paris, 1844. Le mus\u00e9e Louis-Philippe, ch\u00e2teau d\u0027Eu, conserve les deux recueils (inv. 974-19 et 984-6) et un exemplaire de Pingret illustr\u00e9 de lithographies en couleurs. Le fonds de la Maison de France, aux Archives nationales, conserve le recueil de Pingret (300 AP 111 33 bis).","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0.231","displayDimension":"0.231 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0.314","displayDimension":"0.314 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Pastel.","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Acquis en septembre 1926 de Monsieur Rapilly, libraire.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Derni\u00e8re provenance : Rapilly, M.","note":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"startYear":1926,"endYear":null}]}],"ownedBy":"","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"collection":[{"value":"Rapilly, Georges"}],"place":[{"value":"Grande-Bretagne+"},{"value":"Tr\u00e9port, Le"},{"value":"Angleterre+"},{"value":"Windsor, Windsor Castle+"},{"value":"Eu, ch\u00e2teau, mus\u00e9e Louis-Philippe, oeuvre en rapport"},{"value":"Paris, Archives nationales, fonds de la Maison de France, oeuvre en rapport"},{"value":"Windsor+"}],"person":[{"value":"Louis-Philippe Ier, roi des Fran\u00e7ais"},{"value":"Victoria, reine de Grande-Bretagne+"},{"value":"Skelton, oeuvre en rapport"}],"subject":[{"value":"marine"},{"value":"paysage"},{"value":"vaisseau"},{"value":"bateau"},{"value":"Voyage de Louis